      description "Additional definitions from MOM:min/max-elements:0/unbounded;root;systemCreated; A unit that provides support to adjacent units, in terms of power, climate and/or external alarms. RDNs of these MOs are SupportUnit=1, SupportUnit=2 and so on. Autocreated when the support unit is detected by the system.";
